/**
 * Internationalization (i18n) Foundation
 *
 * Type-safe translation system with locale detection,
 * fallback chain, and interpolation support.
 *
 * Pure functions for lookup, formatting, and locale detection.
 * React hook (useTranslation) is client-only — must be used
 * inside 'use client' components only.
 */

